ZH: 一旦出现问题，我们就需要马上解决。
EN: Once a problem arises, we need to solve it immediately.

ZH: 一旦错过这个机会，可能很难再有下次了。
EN: Once you miss this opportunity, it may be difficult to have another chance.

ZH: 一旦你开始迟到，老师会很生气。
EN: Once you start being late, the teacher will get angry.

ZH: 一旦他发脾气，就很难安抚他。
EN: Once he gets angry, it's difficult to appease him.

ZH: 一旦你完成任务，请立即告诉我。
EN: Once you complete the task, please inform me immediately.

ZH: 一旦签订合同，就要履行承诺。
EN: Once the contract is signed, the commitments must be fulfilled.

ZH: 一旦你放弃努力，就不会有进步。
EN: Once you give up on your efforts, there will be no progress.

ZH: 一旦天黑，我们就回家吧。
EN: Once it gets dark, let's go home.

ZH: 一旦你说出去，就无法收回。
EN: Once you say it, you can't take it back.

ZH: 一旦他犯了错误，他会立即道歉。
EN: Once he makes a mistake, he will apologize immediately.

ZH: 一旦你试过，你会喜欢的。
EN: Once you try it, you'll like it.

ZH: 一旦你违反规则，就会受到惩罚。
EN: Once you break the rules, you will be punished.

ZH: 一旦你理解这个概念，你会发现很有用。
EN: Once you understand this concept, you will find it very useful.

ZH: 一旦你习惯了，这个过程就会变得容易。
EN: Once you get used to it, the process will become easier.

ZH: 一旦他决定了，就不会改变主意。
EN: Once he makes a decision, he won't change his mind.

ZH: 一旦你被接受，你就要积极表现。
EN: Once you are accepted, you should perform actively.

ZH: 一旦你开始工作，就不要停下来。
EN: Once you start working, don't stop.

ZH: 一旦你明白了原理，问题就会变得容易解决。
EN: Once you understand the principles, the problems will be easier to solve.

ZH: 一旦你学会了，这个技能会很有用处。
EN: Once you learn it, this skill will be very useful.

ZH: 一旦你走错了方向，就会迷路。
EN: Once you take the wrong direction, you will get lost.

ZH: 一旦你打破了承诺，就会失去信任。
EN: Once you break the promise, you will lose trust.
